public class Carmichael
extends java.lang.Object

A simple class to hold all of the known Carmichael numbers

Author:
Ron Horner

This Carmichael class is an ArrayList of all of the known Carmichael numbers. This list of numbers was found at:

http://de.wikibooks.org/wiki/Pseudoprimzahlen:_Tabelle_Carmichael-Zahlen

It is understood that there are infinitely many Carmichael Numbers, but there are also infintiely many Mersene Primes. However we only know of a finite number of them. So for the purposes of this class, it serves as a safety net for the Fermat primality test.
